title: 2009 May Grand Sumo Tournament (Summer Natsu Basho Tokyo) Day 6
description:
2009 May Grand Sumo Tournament (Summer Natsu Basho Tokyo) Day 6 [English Audio]



This is the Day 6 broadcast with _English Audio_. This is the last day I post the JSTV feed since they cut off the first 30 minutes of the basho. My friend who was providing the JSTV feed was having problems with thier service so I decided to order TV Japan and do it all myself. Starting at Day 10 upto day 15 I will be posting the full 2 hour TV Japan version. The full 15 day July basho will be the full 2 hour broadcast from TV Japan with english audio. Also some people have emailed me regarding the large file size, I can encode the highlight show which has just the bouts and japanese audio at a lower filesize as I did with Day 1. If there is enough interest I will post the full english version and highlight show otherwise I will just stick with the 2 hour english version.



As I am paying for the satellite service I would appreciate donations (costs me $25 USD for the service per month).
